research.initial_task.template:
User task:

{task}

Product Manager research plan:
{pm_research_plan}

Use Tavily Search and Tavily Extract to gather evidence for the Product Manager's plan and the specialist roles below. Start with an adapted research objective checklist, extract real source pages, verify objective coverage, and stop only when enough objectives are covered or configured limits are reached.

{configured_guidance}Available specialist roles:
{role_brief}

Return strict JSON only, no markdown. Required top-level keys: research_summary, objectives, missing_information, research_quality, recommended_next_searches, search_queries, failed_sources, sources. Each objective must include name, status, and evidence. Each evidence item must include objective, claim, source_title, source_url, summary, and confidence. Also include concise role-relevant implications inside objective evidence summaries so downstream agents can use the research.

